It includes optimising your website and content, so that it can rank well when your potential customers search for keywords relevant to your business.</p>\n<p>Working with an SEO consultant will help your customers find your content on search engine result pages, and get rewarded by search engines for quality, consistent content.</p>\n<p>SEO is not a game of instant gratification, it takes time to analyse and execute plans that will improve your rankings. </p>\n<p>There is no turn key solution, to really grasp where the actions can come from, you may need a full audit to understand where gains can be made.
